na dole udariti nozem?!

1093
01:48:07,279 --> 01:48:09,414
Da nije kao u indijskom filmu?!

1094
01:48:09,415 --> 01:48:10,415
Slusajte!

1095
01:48:11,413 --> 01:48:13,698
To je bes!

1096
01:48:15,215 --> 01:48:19,771
To je bes, bes! Sta to pricate?
Nije mogao, indijski film...?!

1097
01:48:21,740 --> 01:48:24,161
Ma, bes! Bes!

1098
01:48:25,727 --> 01:48:32,397
Ja nisam radio kao bolnicar u hitnoj, ali mogu da
Vam pokazem kako nizi covek moze udariti nozem nadole.

1099
01:48:35,026 --> 01:48:36,470
